{"tid":605512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【深夜負能量】每個星期嘅喱個時間都會胡思亂想","createTime":"2018-03-25T17:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T17:37:27.000Z","uid":154116,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19334ed9fdefa16214d2aedcb44d31205ef7af3e","tid":605512,"uid":154116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期日晚嘅12點，個腦就會開始諗聽日返工有咩要做，聽日幾時要幾點先可以收工。<br />\n然後，就會諗做完之後又點。又然後，做到工作要求，屋企人朋友嘅期望，又會點？現實咪就係每晚9點幾10點先返到屋企入房，打陣機同女朋友傾陣電話又一日。<br />\n七日之後又到到星期日晚嘅12點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慢慢個人就開始麻目，無咩事可以令到自己開心。我好記得細個個陣，學識踩單車個種滿足感，露營夜晚睇星個種興奮感覺。而家？我淨係感覺到自己每日都攰，身體差咗，好似每日都等緊死咁。<br />\n<br />\nSorry...1999...有無人都好似我咁，廿幾歲就咁係咪好唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd9acf53914c7d692c1c2713ef63dab657bde0a","tid":605512,"uid":125427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"雖然好sad<br />\n但有女朋友傾下電話<br />\n我覺得都已經好好啦<br />\n今晚sad完 聽日繼續努力陽光啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8478dbbf71d89d378481f2e61a9bfa2dbda9df6a","tid":605512,"uid":154116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fd9acf53914c7d692c1c2713ef63dab657bde0a","tid":605512,"uid":125427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"雖然好sad<br />\n但有女朋友傾下電話<br />\n我覺得都已經好好啦<br />\n今晚sad完 聽日繼續努力陽光啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"試過想樂觀少少，但每晚番到房，望住天花板，就覺得每分每秒都係虛無咁過咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}